Module org.klojang.check
Package org.klojang.check

Class Tag

java.lang.Object
org.klojang.check.Tag
public final class Tag extends Object
String constants for some commonly used names for fields, parameters and variables. To be used as the second argument to the Check.that() methods of the Check class.
